title: Cascading Parameter Values Not Displayed Correctly in HTML Viewer
description: Cascading parameter values are not displayed properly in the HTML viewer.
OB: When using the HTML viewer to preview a design with cascading parameters, the second parameter value in the same cascading parameter group is not displayed.
EB: I expect that when I select the first parameter value, the second parameter value in the same cascading parameter group should be displayed in the HTML viewer.
SR:
To reproduce the issue:
1. Open the attached design file in the HTML viewer.
2. Click on the 'Change Parameter' button in the HTML viewer.
